<crewBlueprint name="rk_weaponlike">
    <desc>(RK Bam) Vexopaths are made by applying electroshocks to a technopath bathed in acid and stuffed with a bomb. Makes it mad and unable to change shape, but able to launch bombs.
		No longer counts as a Technopath or Morph.

	Inherited stats: takes 0.5 crew slot, immune to suffocation, 75% resistance to fire damage and stun, 0.8x movement speed.</desc>
    <cost>55</cost>
    <title>Vexo</title>
    <short>Vexo</short>		<!-- this field doesn't show up anywhere in-game -->
    <rarity>0</rarity>
    <powerList>
		<power>Active Ability: Teleport a 1 damage bomb to the enemy ship, once per jump</power>
		<power>Active Ability: Detonate a 1 damage bomb right here, once per jump [style[color:ff3377]](Has friendly fire)[[/style]]</power>
		<power>Max Health is 80. Is cloned at 2x speed</power>
		<power>Can only move, man, fight, sabotage, teleport</power>
		<power>Learns Weapons and Combat extremely fast</power>
    </powerList>
    <colorList>
        <layer>
            <color r="255" g="255" b="255" a="1"/>
        </layer>
    </colorList>
</crewBlueprint>

