<augBlueprint name="RK_ARROGANCE_SHIELD">
    <title>Arrogance Shield</title>
	<desc>(RK Punk gear) Risky for your Shields but could make you untouchable. Strange cubes died for this.
		
		Adds a 9 hitpoints Super Shield. Stacks with other Super Shields, but not with itself.
		On your ship, your crew-drones also gain 3 HP/second while enemy crew-drones lose that much.
		[style[color:ff3377]]WARNING: Reduces Shield charge speed by 25% and Weapons charge speed by 5%.[[/style]]</desc>
    <cost>120</cost>
    <rarity>5</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="RK_COMBAT_DEFENSE_REMOVER">
    <title>Vulnerabilizer</title>
    <desc>(RK Punk gear) This combat augment slowly weakens the enemy's defenses. Bosses hate it.
		
		Every 3 to 7 seconds (at random), limits enemy Shields and Engines by 1 power. This effect stacks up to 16 times if lucky.
		All effects end after 40 to 75 seconds, based on how many drones you choose to use.
		[Uses 1-2 | and 3 reactor power. Emergency Generator can apply.]</desc>
    <cost>80</cost>
    <rarity>5</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- see 'textless events' in modding tips folder -->
<augBlueprint name="RK_COMBAT_OFFENSE_DISABLER">
    <title>Offense Disabler</title>
    <desc>(RK Punk gear) This combat augment can fully disable enemy offense for 6 seconds. Then, the effect becomes weaker until it's gone at 18 seconds (you will be warned). Perfect against aggressive enemies!
		[Uses 2| and 3 reactor power. Emergency Generator can apply.]

		Affected systems:
		Weapons, Drone Control, Mind Control,
		Hacking, Teleporter, all Artilleries,
		Corruptor (from "Darkest Desire"),
		and Turrets (from "The Old Guard").</desc>
    <cost>70</cost>
    <rarity>4</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- [OUTDATED, Rework below.]
Jump event augment! Code is still in combat augment xml for technical reasons though (is that part OBSO?).
